  mosfet-liquid-widgets-0.9.6_pre4.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  21 Feb 2003; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  Add ~x86 keyword to 0.9.6_pre4, works ok here.

*mosfet-liquid-widgets-0.9.6_pre4 (08 Feb 2003)

